| 2      | 2010-01 | 0.407374 | 0.270169 |
|        | 2010-02 | 0.345566 | 0.931718 |
|        | 2010-02 | 0.042698 | 0.989230 |
|        | 2010-04 | 0.801888 | 0.574477 |

</div>

``` python
lag(df['A'])
```

